author: Paramount Plus
description:
Starting January 2026, you can stream every UFC fight live with your Paramount+ subscription.

Catch MMA's biggest stars squaring off in numbered events, and follow future champions as they climb the ranks in weekly Fight Nights.

Hit docuseries like UFC Countdown and UFC Embedded set the stage for upcoming fights with interviews and training camp access. Miss a bout? No sweat. You can find replays and highlights for every event.

UFC fans, say goodbye to Pay-Per-View, and hello to Paramount+. Stream every fight live!

Like Paramount+ on Facebook: https://bit.ly/PPlusFacebook
Follow Paramount+ on X: https://bit.ly/PPlusOnX
Follow Paramount+ on Instagram: https://bit.ly/PPlusInstagram
Follow Paramount+ on Threads: https://bit.ly/PPlusThreads
Follow Paramount+ on TikTok: https://bit.ly/PPlusTikTok
